043700******************************************************************
043800*
043900 030-E-NOVAPLACA.
044000*
044100
044200     MOVE    0                       TO      CH-NOTF.
044300
044400     LOCK    NOVAPLACSE1             AT
044500             NPL-PLACA               EQUAL   IN-PLACA
