044800             MOVE 1                  TO      CH-NOTF
044850         ELSE
044900             DISPLAY "PC/GEV/T435/DB - LOCK ERROR NOVAPLACSE1"
045100             PERFORM 200-E-ERRODB    THRU        200-S-ERRODB
